/*------------------------------------------------------------------ 
 MBlue Simple-Gray Top-Toolbar (Ver. 0.3.5)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Author: M.BLUE - Tested on: Firefox 3.0.5 - Last Update: 27.07.2008
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
 Transforms "some" Toolbar Buttons into Tabs-like Buttons if moved
 inside of the Menubar.
 Integrates better with the Simple-Gray Theme.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
What it does:
 - Create tabbed-like buttons for some specific extension icons
 - Create a tabbed-like look for the Firefox menubar
 - Create a tabbed-like look and combine the cut-copy-paste buttons
 - Create a tabbed-like look for the "Foxclocks" estension
 - Create a tabbed-like look for the "ForecastFox" estension
 - Fix the "Video Download Helper" icon that moves when active
 - Create a button for "Piclens" that change colors when active
 - Create a button for "ABP" that change color when state changes
 - Create a button for "IE Tab" that change color when state changes
 - Create a button for "stylish" and "DownThemALL"
 - Create a button for the Throbber
 - Nav-buttons aligned to other buttons when inside the menubar*
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Supported Extensions:
 Foxclocks, Video Download Helper, Piclens, ADBlockPlus, Stylish,
 DownThemALL, IETab.

 Also supports standard icons (Bookmarks, History, Addons,
 Downloads, etc.) and some Extension (Tab Sidebar, TagSifter, etc.)
 but without any special effect.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Note:
 Set small icons to get it to work.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Integrates with:
 MBlue Simple-Gray Theme
 MBlue Simple-Gray Theme Ext-Support
 MBlue Simple-Gray Sidebar
 MBlue Simple-Gray Sidebar Ext-Support
 MBlue Simple-Gray Slim-Download
 MBlue Simple-Gray Slim-Extension
 MBlue Simple-Gray Buttons
>MBlue Simple-Gray Top-Toolbar
 MBlue Simple-Gray Popup
 MBlue Simple-Gray Statusbar Icon
 MBlue Combine Nav-Buttons Vista*
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Updates:
 27.07.2008 Ver. 0.3.5 = new version
 21.07.2008 Ver. 0.3.1 = added support for DTA and IE Tab,
                         added support for more buttons
 19.07.2008 Ver. 0.3.0 = added support for cut-copy-paste buttons,
                         font size and menubar changed
 18.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.5 = working on new version
 11.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.2 = small fixes
  9.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.1 = Download Helper 3.1.1 released, adjusted
  8.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.0 = ready to release I guess
  6.07.2008 Ver. 0.1.9 = better integration with Nav-Buttons
  5.07.2008 Ver. 0.1.8 = added ForecastFox support,
                         improved integration with Simple-Gray
  4.07.2008 Ver. 0.1.7 = added the Throbber support,
                         removed the MenuBar hover effect,
                         added support for more icons
  3.07.2008 Ver. 0.1.6 = code optimized
  1.07.2008 Ver. 0.1.5 = background changed
 30.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.4 = now it applies only when icons are small
 29.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.3 = added ABlockPlus & Stylish Support
 27.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.2 = fixed Download Helper icon
 26.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.1 = added Download Helper & Piclens support
 23.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.0 = Menubar & Foxclocks supported
------------------------------------------------------------------*/



